<p><b>lpcwstrAccountName
(variable): </b>A null-terminated character string that holds the name of the
fax account. The account name that <b>lpcwstrAccountName</b> indicates MUST be
in one of the following formats.</p>
<dl>
<dd>
<table><thead>
  <tr>
   <th>
   <p>Format</p>
   </th>
   <th>
   <p>Description</p>
   </th>
  </tr>
 </thead><tbody><tr>
  <td>&lt;machine_name&gt;\&lt;user_name&gt;</td>
  <td>For a local user with machine_name as the local machine&#39;s name.</td>
 </tr><tr>
  <td>&lt;domain_name&gt;\&lt;user_name&gt;</td>
  <td>For a remote (not local) user.</td>
 </tr></tbody></table>
